name:            gsl-random
version:         0.1.1
homepage:        http://stat.stanford.edu/~patperry/code/gsl-random
synopsis:        Bindings the the GSL random number generation facilities.
description:
    Bindings to the GNU Scientific Library random number generators and random
    distributions.
    .
